OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVery warm
OL,6,Finto the evening, with late sunshine
OL,7,Finland and some low cloud near some
OL,8,Fcoastal districts. Sporadic showery
OL,9,Frain and some thundery outbreaks will
OL,10,Fspread northeast later in the night,
OL,11,Fwith strong, gusty winds, hail and
OL,12,Fdownpours possible locally.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FGusty, thundery downpours
OL,15,Fpossible initially and to a more
OL,16,Flimited extent later. Becoming
OL,17,Fexceptionally hot, markedly hotter
OL,18,Fthan Thursday in eastern areas. The
OL,19,Fsunshine generally perhaps
OL,20,Fperiodically hazy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
